                    <h3>Ontario Traffic Ticket Violations</h3>
                    <hr/>
                    <p>The penalty for speeding tickets in Ontario goes beyond the demerit points or paying the fine. Convictions on Speeding Tickets will cause your driving privileges to be revoked, if you are a Novice Driver and cause your insurance rates to be affected to the point of non-affordability.</p>
                    <h4 class="first">What you’re not being told about how to Fight Speeding Tickets</h4>
                    <p>What you’re not being told about how to fight Speeding Tickets is an Ontario Speeding Ticket is considered to be an absolute liability which means the Prosecution does not have to prove that you intended to speed to obtain a conviction. In fighting a Speeding Ticket, it only has to be proven that you were driving beyond the prescribed (posted) limit. However, this does not mean that you are guilty.</p>
                    <p>The most effective way to fight Speeding Tickets in Ontario is to hire a Speeding Ticket Lawyer, Speeding Ticket Attorney or a Licensed Paralegal. The immediate benefit in doing so is the achievement of the withdrawal of the Speeding Ticket Charge.              </p>
                    <p>Get Legal Help utilizes case law, video evidence, experienced Speeding Ticket Attorneys, X-Copps and Traffic Ticket Paralegals to remove speeding points, and reduce speeding ticket fines. We have dismissed speeding tickets in Ontario, for our clients and have the well-respected ability to successfully fight speeding ticket Toronto and in all Ontario Provincial Offences Court locations. We are not afraid to take on Speeding Ticket no points when many firms state, “Sorry we can’t help you.” The reason being is we do not go to the Ontario Provincial Courts to simply plead guilty for you. This is something you           can do yourself. When you hire Get Legal Help to fight a speeding ticket, we intend to win your case for you.</p>
